<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.208971>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Zeuxoides troncosoi sp. nov., female: A, holotype, dorsal. B, pleotelson. C, antennule. D, antenna." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/208971/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.208972>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Zeuxoides troncosoi sp. nov., A, labrum. B, right mandible. C, left mandible. D, detail of mandibular molar. E, labium (only half figured). F, maxillule. G, maxillular palp. H, epignath. I, maxilliped. J, maxilliped endite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/208972/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.208973>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Zeuxoides troncosoi sp. nov., A, female cheliped. B, detail of the female chela. C-H, pereopods 1 – 6 respectively. I, pleopod 1. J, uropod." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/208973/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.208974>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Zeuxoides troncosoi sp. nov., male: A, allotype, dorsal. B, cheliped. C, coxa 1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/208974/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

